"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-news-world-1902789-volocity-paris-olympics-flying-taxis\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Incredible flying taxis could ferry people to the Olympics for \\u00a3250 each.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 75, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"German company Volocopter manufactures the \\\"VoloCity\\\", an electric aircraft aiming to be used at the Paris Olympics this summer.\", \"from\": 77, \"to\": 205, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 77, \"end\": 83, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"score\": 0.47956204680966924, \"rank\": 0.6848980903841235, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The VoloCity is a two-seater aircraft (including the pilot's seat) equipped with batteries powering 18 rotors arranged in a ring above the cockpit.\", \"from\": 207, \"to\": 354, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To carry paying passengers, the VoloCity will have to obtain certification from the European Aviation Safety Agency (EASA).\", \"from\": 356, \"to\": 479, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 440, \"end\": 478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Union_Aviation_Safety_Agency\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"European Aviation Safety Agency (EASA)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Union_Aviation_Safety_Agency\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Union_Aviation_Safety_Agency\"}, {\"begin\": 440, \"end\": 478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Union_Aviation_Safety_Agency\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"European Aviation Safety Agency (EASA)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Union_Aviation_Safety_Agency\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Union_Aviation_Safety_Agency\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Promotors are hoping to try them out during the Olympic and Paralympic Games, but aiming for certification by the European authorities in the autumn.\", \"from\": 481, \"to\": 630, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"READ MORE:Eurostar tipped for huge new multi-million plan to add more routes    The VoloCity has been described by Volocopter as a \\\"game changer\\\" that will transport people between transport hubs \\\"whisper-quiet and emission-free\\\" for \\\"seamless, faster, and more convenient options\\\".\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 914, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 642, \"end\": 650, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"score\": 0.9999999999902229, \"rank\": 9.828642934844752e-12, \"text\": \"Eurostar\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\"}, {\"begin\": 747, \"end\": 757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Volocopter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Volocopter\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Volocopter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Volocopter\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris airports operator, ADP Group, has joined forces with the \\u00cele-de-France region and Volocopter to demonstrate the feasibility of this new mode of transport, which is designed to link different take-off and landing sites known as \\\"vertiports\\\".\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 1166, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 920, \"end\": 925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.6021934642048896e-18, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 945, \"end\": 948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Groupe_ADP\", \"score\": 0.999994246484856, \"rank\": 5.622863235454247e-06, \"text\": \"ADP\", \"types\": [\"